    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This collector-grade example boasts a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed per preventative maintenance protocols. The chassis dynamics are exceptionally sharp, featuring a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup with zero bushing deflection. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle represents a peak era of longitudinal, naturally aspirated performance with zero deferred maintenance.",
